2000;;The Ladies Man;;American;;Reginald Hudlin;;Tim Meadows, Billy Dee Williams, Will Ferrell;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Ladies_Man;;Herbert H. Heebert (Jerry Lewis) is a young man who loses his girlfriend, swears off romance, and then takes a job at a genteel, women-only boarding house, run by Helen Wellenmellen (Helen Traubel). Although most of the women treat him like a servant, Fay (Pat Stanley) helps him with his fear of women.